viously, our exclusive designs channel is financially advantageous to whole=
sale, but we=E2=80=99ve really spent the last few years being a lot more di=
sciplined in how we manage our cash. Since we I.P.O.=E2=80=99d, we=E2=80=99=
ve had to change how we operate as a company, change the margins of the bus=
iness, bring down our cash burn, and get the business into a healthy positi=
on. A lot of the
work that we did in =E2=80=9922 to =E2=80=9924 to change the financials has=
 enabled us now to invest back into our customers in a huge way via invento=
ry.

