Is the turmoil in the department store world benefiting RTR? Are brands now
relying more on RTR than on multi-brand retail chains?=C2=A0

=C2=A0

Trust is everything in this industry, and I=E2=80=99m sure that we benefite=
d from the fact that there=E2=80=99s just a lot of chaos in the industry an=
d we=E2=80=99ve been this trusted partner for over 15 years. And you could =
really deliver one of two things to a brand. You could deliver huge sales n=
umbers, which with some of our brands, we do. But the second thing you coul=
d
deliver is customer acquisition. Given the constant fluctuations they=E2=80=
=99ve had to experience over the last few years=E2=80=94with everything rel=
ated to Farfetch and Matches, and now what=E2=80=99s happening with departm=
ent stores=E2=80=94brands have had to put more pressure, in many cases, on =
their D.T.C. businesses.

Fundamentally, Rent the Runway has brought the traditional retail store int=
o someone=E2=80=99s home. We make it really easy for the customer to try th=
ings risk-free=E2=80=94the average customer is now trying over 50
brands a year from us. She has an organic experience wearing the brand, whi=
ch we know is critical for a lot of these brands.

What=E2=80=99s the value prop for brands to partner with Rent the Runway?

I think the analogy here is actually Sephora. This is what I aspire to be. =
Seven or eight years ago, Sephora changed their strategy from having all of=
 the blockbuster brands on their platform to one where they were going to s=
howcase indie brands and ensure that they were a
discovery engine for beauty, so that people come into that store multiple t=
imes a week, whether online or in person. We=E2=80=99ve become this entirel=
y new marketing channel for coveted brands to acquire future customers of a=
ll ages, and I think the brands are seeing this in their data. So the hotte=
st brands in the world are coming to us now because they see us as a market=
ing opportunity, and a place where customers can really find the latest and=
 greatest in designer fashion in constant rotation.

=E2=80=8A

