s his Mexico tariff policy as a triumph, claiming that his
negotiation tactics curbed fentanyl trafficking, and overlooking the fact t=
hat he has waffled on their imposition.<br/><br/>A key clarification: Curre=
nt tariffs apply to where items are <em>produced</em>, not <em>shipped from=
</em>. This is a common source of confusion among consumers, which is why s=
