her retailers would decide whether to cover the tariffs by baking the extra=
 cost into the retail price or having the customer personally pay the duty =
when they pick up the item at the Post Office=E2=80=94it depends who is ide=
ntified as the =E2=80=9Cimporter of record.=E2=80=9D<br/><br/>For now at le=
ast, European luxury products remain unaffected, and the $800 <em>de minimi=
